Definition: the basic human power of intelligent thought and perception
Example: he used his wits to get ahead; I was scared out of my wits; he still had all his marbles and was in full possession of a lively mind
Synonyms: marbles, intelligence, the, basic, human, power, of, intelligent, thought, and, perception, he, used, his, to, get, ahead, I, was, scared, out, my, still, had, all, in, full, possession, a, lively, mind
Category: noun.cognition
